                                    <strong>North:</strong> Prince George, Fort St.
                                    John, Dawson Creek, Terrace, Prince Rupert, Kitimat,
                                    Smithers, Williams Lake, Quesnel.<br />
                                    <strong>Kootenays:</strong> Cranbrook, Nelson,
                                    Castlegar, Trail, Fernie, Invermere, Revelstoke,
                                    Golden.<br />
                                    <strong>Others:</strong> Powell River, Tofino,
                                    Ucluelet, Haida Gwaii, Tumbler Ridge.
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
