                                RS
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">
                                    From Surrey to Smithers
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                                    Retail Manager (TEER 2)
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p
